casebody.data:
Wednesday, March 22, 1989

MERIT DOCKET

89-81. State, ex rel. Davis, v. Court of Common Pleas of Summit Cty.

In Procedendo. On answer of respondent. Answer of respondent treated as motion to dismiss. Motion to dismiss sustained. Cause dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
